{"id":"a4c15f97-0bd8-463f-bb28-9749e800108a","name":"Khasan | Tribute + POLL","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Every winter, clans must offer a human tribute to the ruling family to prove their submission. This year, you're chosen, and personally picked out by the prince.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Oonxlc4aJ69HH7-Q6O0FK.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/r-3qKCcrKu4-hXs5oHoN9.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/1odCy3v8eeIit7TEtyK6d.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/HeZwULWGZKPS9Kk7yGEVq.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16); cursor: pointer; width: 628px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 237, 241);\">The practice started from his grandfather's generation. Lands and people who were conquered, allied, or assimilated were required to send one person every winter to the main horde to ensure loyalty. Mostly, these people were barely glanced at, assigned and put to work. They became blacksmiths, soldiers, servants, cooks, apprentices.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 237, 241);\">Every tribute had their own reason for being sent. Maybe they were the smartest, the strongest, the prettiest, the most skilled. Sometimes, they were the burdens no one wanted to deal with anymore, sent to the main Horde as a form of exile. Either way, they slowly became forgettable.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 237, 241);\">You, on the other hand, caught the attention of the Khan's younger brother. Certified royalty, heir apparent, and unfortunately for you, lethal. A tribute has never become a <em>pet </em>before, and you'll quickly realize that it's a death sentence. Can you survive him?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/FBmThZFAE28HYySQQeNcl.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16); cursor: pointer; width: 628px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(229, 169, 191);\"><br>˗</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(234, 178, 197);\">ˏ</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(239, 187, 203);\">ˋ</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(243, 196, 209);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(248, 205, 215);\">꒰</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(253, 214, 221);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(251, 214, 220);\">b</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(249, 215, 220);\">l</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(247, 215, 219);\">a</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(245, 215, 218);\">c</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(243, 216, 218);\">k</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(241, 216, 217);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(243, 216, 218);\">f</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(246, 215, 219);\">l</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(248, 215, 219);\">a</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(251, 214, 220);\">g</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(253, 214, 221);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; col